languages.text: "I have come because the Prince wills it. The souls of all his progenitors belong to him alone. None will escape his embrace."

« Je suis ici par la volonté du Prince. Les âmes de ces géniteurs n'appartiennent qu'à lui. Nul ne peut échapper à son étreinte. »

languages.text: 「私が来たのは皇子の意志によるものだ。先祖の魂はすべて彼だけのもの。誰も彼の抱擁から逃れることはできない」
languages.original_text: "I have come because the Prince wills it. The souls of all his progenitors belong to him alone. None will escape his embrace."

languages.text: “我来这里，是出于王子的意愿。他那些先祖的灵魂只属于他，没人能逃脱他的怀抱。”
languages.original_text: "I have come because the Prince wills it. The souls of all his progenitors belong to him alone. None will escape his embrace."

traits.locale_text: “我来这里，是出于王子的意愿。他那些先祖的灵魂只属于他，没人能逃脱他的怀抱。”

languages.text: "Ich bin gekommen, weil der Prinz es wünscht. Die Seelen all seiner Nachfahren gehören ihm allein. Niemand wird seiner Umarmung entkommen."
languages.original_text: "I have come because the Prince wills it. The souls of all his progenitors belong to him alone. None will escape his embrace."

languages.text: «He venido porque es la voluntad del Príncipe. Las almas de todos sus progenitores le pertenecen a él y solo a él. Nadie escapará a su abrazo».

languages.text: "Buraya geldim çünkü Prens böyle diledi. Tüm atalarının ruhu, yalnızca ona aittir. Kucaklamasından kimse kaçamaz."
